channel.title: How do I get onto IRC chat?
channel.description: How do I get into Dodian.com's Irc chat when I go to enter. All I get is, Windows need your permission to continue. I click ok then it comes up with Windows has blocked this program Javairc/ for your own safety. Or something like that, How do I get my computer to let me go on it.
